0751198876734, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}, {\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Sosa\", \"score\": 0.9999999951314749, \"rank\": 3.80855846238563e-09, \"text\": \"Sosa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Sosa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sammy_Sosa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Double victor Camilo Vera of Colombia, Xiang Yina of China, Nishiyama Misa of Japan, Ojima Nao of Japan and AIN Arsenii Dukhno captured titles on the second of two days of apparatus finals at the Junior World Championships in Manila on Monday.\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3576, \"end\": 3582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camilo_Sanvezzo\", \"score\": 0.9065473129504692, \"rank\": 0.10308638690218921, \"text\": \"Camilo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camilo_Sanvezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camilo_Sanvezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.856168221378506e-17, \"text\": \"Vera\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\"}, {\"begin\": 3615, \"end\": 3620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.730643416643907, \"rank\": 0.3683087729013643, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3640, \"end\": 3645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8480029282353824, \"rank\": 0.10692765182763554, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3670, \"end\": 3673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AIN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 3788, \"end\": 3794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9999424717538988, \"rank\": 5.7507732117895954e-05, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China and the U.S. each claimed two golds, and an AIN gymnast took the fifth title, on the first of two days of apparatus finals at the Junior World Championships in Manila on Sunday.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3807, \"end\": 3812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.730643416643907, \"rank\": 0.3683087729013643, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3857, \"end\": 3860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999836368262, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AIN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Independent_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.999942